            "â€¢ <strong>Balanced funds</strong> - own both stocks and bonds in {{STATE_NAME}}",
            "â€¢ <strong>Target-date funds</strong> - automatically adjust based on retirement date in {{STATE_NAME}}",
            "<strong>Key consideration:</strong> Expense ratios (annual fees) compound over time - a 1% fee difference can cost you 25% of your wealth over 30 years! in {{STATE_NAME}}",
